  <preface>
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <para>
      Buzztard aims to be a succesor of the freeware music tracker calld Buzz.
      The development of Buzz has been discontinued as the author lost all his source-codes.
    </para>
    <para>
      The homepage of the buzztard project can be found at
      <ulink url="http://www.buzztard.org">www.buzztard.org</ulink>.
      It is based on a wiki and used to draft further development.
    </para>
  </preface>
  
